			<h3>What if I currently have money in MSFT or BrokerageLink?</h3>
			<p>In the Microsoft 401k Plan, the MSFT common stock and BrokerageLink options are essentially managed as separate accounts.  As such, you will first have to move money out of those, and then rebalance as a second step.</p>
